project:
Greetings Bandit

Welcome to the Battle for the Beach

Help reclaim land on the beach
ready for our turtles to lay their eggs. 

The game is simple:

1) Roll the die
2) Place your piece on the hex grid
3) Then it's the Ai's turn

Rules:

> Can only place pieces down if they are touching your 
  currently placed pieces or if you're on the first move, the left side of the hex grid.

> Cells on your side of the board are worth 1 point and cells on your opposition's side are worth 2 points. Game ends when a player is unable to place a piece. 

Good luck!

Click the button below to begin.
